{"tid":1592661,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解宜家冇人理個柒婆","createTime":"2019-09-24T17:09:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T17:40:26.000Z","uid":320223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"05242f0ea923454dc3fe8eca7f33fb7babcbd3a5","tid":1592661,"uid":320223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:09:31.000Z","msg":"其實個柒婆係罪魁禍首 可唔可以搵人keep住屌鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一切事情既發生都係因為林奠而起 佢唔搞咁多野就唔會變成宜家咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推埋啲戇鳩policy出黎搵狗黎擋箭 打壓我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然我知大家都屌到悶同冇野好屌 但都希望大家仲記得係邊撚個搞到宜家香港咁撚樣阿屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n核爆都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6669c5eba26eca5aac93a507ca44b3435ae46456","tid":1592661,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:09:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"922c279a729e2032dc810844c0c5699a1c208390","tid":1592661,"uid":261530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:10:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d419d534e3aed172ff337e801a275b665aa8fe7","tid":1592661,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:40:26.000Z","msg":"[文宣] 我哋好似忘記咗其中一條重要戰線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592692</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}